data.description: Welcome to 302 E Meyer Ave. Enjoy large rooms with beautiful hardwood floors. Spacious closets and plenty of storage. Have friends and family over for dinner in the beautiful dining room which leads right into the large living room. The bedrooms have closet space galore! Outside you will find a beautiful deck and covered porch on the side. The third floor is perfect for use as a game room, office, you name it.  Make 302 E Meyer Ave yours today!
